aptivity because their relations were not been able to raise the ransom demanded by the bandits.  The kidnapping cases in and around Idon ward of Kajuru are becoming a recurring event that has led to the impoverishment of the people of the affected communities who have to do away with their life savings and farm produce to pay ransom to redeem their loved ones from ‘unknown’ gunmen who victimised them at will,” he said.   Governor of Kaduna State, Nasir El-Rufai. By Ibrahim Hassan-Wuyo Terrorists who kidnapped locals at Anguwan Bulus in Chikun Local Government Area of Kaduna State have killed three of the victims and threatened to kill more unless a ransom is paid. Spokesperson for the Kaduna State Police Command, ASP Mohammed Jalige,… In "Metro" Bandits By Ibrahim Hassan-Wuyo Terrorists, who kidnapped locals at Anguwan Bulus in Chikun Local Government Area of Kaduna State, have reportedly killed three of the victims and threatened to kill more unless ransom is paid. The bandits attacked the Anguwan Bulus community killing one local and abducting several others. They… In "Metro" By Ibrahim Hassan-Wuyo  Family members of kidnapped former Head of Department ( HOD) with the Kaduna Polytechnic ( KADPOLY), Engineer  Ramatu Abarshi, have alleged that stories that emanated from the social media on the kidnap incidence is almost jeopardizing the lives of Ramatu and her daughter.  It was alleged that the… In "News"